{"data":[{"date":"15:13 16/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nepal v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1 Nepal cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 b\u1ea3ng D, v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c di\u1ec5n ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Nepal \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1eb1ng \u0110T Olympic Nepal r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd &nbsp;Kathmandu&nbsp;c\u1ee7a Nepal&nbsp;nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 ngay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh, th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Asian Cup t\u1ea1i Incheon 2013, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nepal v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-0 v\u00e0 2-0&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y d\u1eabn l\u1eddi tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV \u0110T Olympic Nepal, Bal Gopal Maharja cho r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. &ldquo;&ldquo;M\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Nepal. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 cu\u1ed7m \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb tay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c Nepal c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1edfi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pakistan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u1edbi 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf hai k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y trong khi Nepal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Asiad . H\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn thua Kuwait 1-3 n\u0103m 1982 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 65 b\u00e0n trong c\u00e1c l\u1ea7n g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd t\u1edbi xem, ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-0 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain h\u00f4m qua 15/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194590.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: &ldquo;Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5563","checkdouble":"194610"},{"date":"15:32 16/08","title":"Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u201c3 t\u1ec7\u201d t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/olympic-nepal-la-doi-bong-3-te-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Nepal l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ASIAD khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu 3 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i n\u00e0y.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nepal t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao khi tham gia s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng 161 tr\u00ean BXH FIFA.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD n\u0103m nay, Nepal \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-1. D\u1eabu sao \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 3 t\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Nepal l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng 3 t\u1ec7 t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Nhan-dinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal,-(19h-ngay-168)-Duy-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Olympic Nepal t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Nepal to\u00e0n thua trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD. N\u0103m 1982, h\u1ecd thua 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (ghi 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 9 l\u1ea7n).\u00a0T\u1edbi k\u1ef3 ASIAD n\u0103m 1986, h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 17 b\u00e0n thua). <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m 1994, Nepal ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i thua 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 20 b\u00e0n thua). \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n, tr\u1eadn thua 0-11 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c khi \u1ea5y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eadm nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ASIAD t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 1998, Nepal l\u1ea1i thua 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 5 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi). \u0110\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2002, h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u00e0m b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn 3 l\u1ea7n (0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, 13 b\u00e0n thua).\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho t\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 17 tr\u1eadn thua trong 17 tr\u1eadn tham d\u1ef1 \u1edf ASIAD. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia duy nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i ASIAD. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nepal c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t ASIAD v\u1edbi 64 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi trong l\u1ecbch s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u2018th\u00e0nh t\u00edch\u2019, kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u hi v\u1ecdng cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay 16/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nepal v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1 Nepal cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc-168-194601.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd t\u1edbi xem, ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-0 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain h\u00f4m qua 15/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-nepal-truong-thanh-tu-hoc-vien-bong-da-tottenham-quyet-tam-xe-luoi-bui-tien-dung-168-194596.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/sao-nepal-truong-thanh-tu-hoc-vien-bong-da-tottenham-quyet-tam-xe-luoi-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-nepal-truong-thanh-tu-hoc-vien-bong-da-tottenham-quyet-tam-xe-luoi-bui-tien-dung-168-194596.html\">Sao tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tottenham \u0111e d\u1ecda Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nG\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Olympic Nepal \u0111ang t\u1ecf r\u00f5 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ghi b\u00e0n trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194590.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-168-194590.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \u201cNepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo\u201d</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5562","checkdouble":"194611"},{"date":"15:46 16/08","title":"B\u00e1o Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.\r\n\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Pakistan sau c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap\u00a0th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang t\u1ea1m \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng D nh\u1edd h\u01a1n Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5.</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n trong n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean c\u1ea1nh tranh cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ebd tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-Co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D. \u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c n\u00e0y, t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Ifeng \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Sau khi th\u1eafng Pakistan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Do Nepal b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng xem nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m ch\u1eafc trong tay Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00f2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i, n\u00ean Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ec9nh b\u1ea3ng\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng quan \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean, t\u1edd Sina c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201c\u1ede gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1 qu\u00e2n. H\u1ecd gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean b\u1ed9 khung \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn Asiad, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed5 sung ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i. D\u00f9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng ai c\u0169ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1ea7n ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng Nepal 1-0\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t cu\u1ed1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo mong ch\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal-472-194608.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/cu-vung-tin-olympic-viet-nam-thua-suc-ha-guc-olympic-nepal-472-194608.html\">C\u1ee9 v\u1eefng tin, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eeba s\u1ee9c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Olympic Nepal</span><br>\r\nC\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Nepal l\u00fac 19h h\u00f4m nay. Nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam \u00c1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 r\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ef1ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal: Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5561","checkdouble":"194614"},{"date":"16:24 16/08","title":"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 16/8, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng D.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Pakistan sau c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Bao-Pakistan-noi-gi-ve-tran-Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Pakistan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao l\u00e0 Nepal. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Lee Young-jin cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng Nepal \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nepal t\u1ecf ra v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc. Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal\u201d, \u00f4ng Lee n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd\u00a0Yonhap News\u00a0c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Nepal l\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng 161 tr\u00ean BXH FIFA, trong khi c\u1ee7a Pakistan l\u00e0 201 c\u00f2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 102 n\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p coi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Nepal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 6-3-1. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Gyotoku s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \"\u0111\u1ed5 b\u00ea t\u00f4ng\" tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1edfi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111ang th\u1eafng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-nepal-thua-nhan-suc-manh-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194610.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Nepal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nepal v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c gia Nam \u00c1 Nepal cho r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-168-194598.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</span></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5560","checkdouble":"194615"},{"date":"17:09 16/08","title":"B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 bao nhi\u00eau?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/29/bang-xep-hang-fifa-thang-82018-viet-nam-dung-thu-bao-nhieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi FIFA v\u1eeba c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn \u1edf nh\u00f3m d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-tran-dau-asiad-2018-372-194609.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 (Asiad 2018)</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Nepal: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal b\u1ea3ng B m\u00f4n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng 6 h\u1ea1ng, v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018 v\u1edbi 1726 \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1ecf xa nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1edbi 14 b\u1eadc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup v\u1eeba qua c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn tr\u00ean BXH FIFA. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Croatia t\u0103ng 16 b\u1eadc \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1edbi 1643 \u0111i\u1ec3m, ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp sau hai \u0110T B\u1ec9 (1723 \u0111i\u1ec3m) v\u00e0 Brazil (1657 \u0111i\u1ec3m).<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 82018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 bao nhi\u00eau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 82018 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 bao nhi\u00eau h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/29/bxh-fifa-thang-52018-dt-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-thang-hang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean h\u1ea1ng 102 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Croatia l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 Uruguay (t\u0103ng 9 b\u1eadc), Anh (t\u0103ng 6 b\u1eadc), B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (gi\u00e0m 3 b\u1eadc), Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 (gi\u1ea3m 2 b\u1eadc), T\u00e2y Ban Nha (t\u0103ng 1 b\u1eadc). \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong t\u1ed1p 10 v\u1edbi 1580 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i World Cup gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH FIFA th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u1eeba qua l\u1ea1i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina c\u0169ng t\u1ee5t 6 b\u1eadc xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng 11 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Chile t\u1ee5t 3 b\u1eadc xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng 12 hay Ba Lan t\u1ee5t nh\u1eefng 10 b\u1eadc xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng 18. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ef1u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup Italia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng 21, t\u1ee5t 2 b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng FIFA th\u00e1ng 8/2018 c\u0169ng ghi nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup \u0110T Nga. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u0103ng 21 b\u1eadc \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 49. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah v\u1eeba l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u01a1i \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t (77 \u0111i\u1ec3m), v\u1eeba l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t h\u1ea1ng kinh kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t (20 b\u1eadc, xu\u1ed1ng th\u1ee9 65).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, \u0110T Iran v\u1edbi 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. H\u1ecd \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 32 v\u1edbi 1471 \u0111i\u1ec3m, t\u0103ng 5 b\u1eadc so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai l\u00e0 \u00dac v\u1edbi 1431 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ea1ng 43 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u1ea1ng 55 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 102 tr\u00ean BXH, ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0 Philippines\u00a0(h\u1ea1ng 115), Th\u00e1i Lan (h\u1ea1ng 122), Myanmar (138). Brunei l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 v\u1edbi h\u1ea1ng 195 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal-168-194615.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-hlv-park-hang-seo-canh-bao-olympic-viet-nam-truoc-tran-gap-nepal-168-194615.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 16/8, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban-168-194614.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-trung-quoc-tin-tuong-olympic-viet-nam-se-xep-tren-nhat-ban-168-194614.html\">B\u00e1o Trung Qu\u1ed1c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Trung Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5559","checkdouble":"194618"},{"date":"14:15 16/08","title":"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau bi\u1ebft bao n\u1ed7i \u0111au tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, Atletico Madrid cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-2 \u1edf Estonia. \u0110i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u n\u0103m 2018?</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Diego Costa</b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, Diego Costa kho\u00e1c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5m \u00e1o s\u1ed1 19 \u01b0a th\u00edch v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i n\u1ed1t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng trung phong xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh t\u00f3m g\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong kho\u1ea3n \u201cb\u1eaft n\u1ea1t\u201d Sergio Ramos, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia v\u1ed1n mang danh k\u1ebb chuy\u00ean \u0111i b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c, c\u1ea3 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng l\u1eabn d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Du-am-tran-Real-Madrid-vs-Atletico-tranh-Sieu-Cup-Chau-Au-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018: Diego Costa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Costa c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm \u1edf ngay gi\u00e2y 49 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed5 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 13 n\u0103m nay, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paolo Maldini thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League n\u0103m 2005 gi\u1eefa AC Milan v\u00e0 Liverpool.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, v\u1edbi pha \u0111\u00e1nh h\u01a1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00fang b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Angel Correa.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Atletico g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, n\u01a1i Costa ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 ba v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1ea5m ch\u00ecm \u0110KV\u0110 Champions League, mang danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 Wanda Metropolitano.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Sergio Ramos<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Atletico m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V trung l\u1eadp theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, Sergio Ramos.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m derby th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4, trung v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi sang Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea1nh kh\u00f3e \u00f4ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebb th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, sau khi n\u0103m l\u1ea7n b\u1ea3y l\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1ecb HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Liverpool ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Mohamed Salah v\u00e0 Loris Karius trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng N\u0103m v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-Sieu-Cup-Chau-Au-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018: Sergio Ramos</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn 10 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, Ramos v\u1eabn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1ea1o v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i trong b\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c, Ramos nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Real Madrid tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1ebf ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1ef1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Sevilla th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u1ea3n l\u00f2ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00e2u k\u00e9o khi\u1ebfn Costa kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef n\u1ed5i b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh m\u00e0 va ch\u1ea1m.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i trong hi\u1ec7p hai khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Cristiano Ronaldo, Ramos nghi\u1ec5m nhi\u00eam ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n penalty v\u00e0 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t 11m, anh t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1eeba Jan Oblak \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng cho Los Blancos.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 quay ra b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Ramos, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00e0n \u0103n m\u1eebng t\u1ef1 m\u00e3n nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh c\u00fap. Sau c\u00f9ng, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o b\u1edfi anh \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1edbi th\u00eam ba b\u00e0n thua, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng cho ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam bu\u1ed3n.<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-184-194585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-184-194585.html\">Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico: Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam</span><br>\r\nN\u1ed7i nh\u1edb l\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t sau tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ed9 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Saul Niguez<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a v\u00e0 k\u00e9o v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Real Madrid v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi \u01b0u th\u1ebf th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i \u1edf th\u1eddi gian cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p hai.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-Sieu-Cup-Chau-Au-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018: Saul Niguez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u00edt ai ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, khi Atletico v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Saul Niguez \u2013 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa b\u1eaft volley tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i r\u00eca v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1eeba ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 29 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 29 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Atletico \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 100%, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 h\u00f2a c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00e2y, Saul c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh 8 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng knock-out tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o Los Rojiblancos c\u0169ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">C\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t \u201cg\u00e0 son\u201d t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh l\u1edbn? Better call Saul! (\u201cH\u00e3y g\u1ecdi cho Saul!\u201d \u2013 t\u00ean m\u1ed9t series phim truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a M\u1ef9).<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Keylor Navas<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Khi t\u00e2n binh Thibaut Courtois ch\u01b0a s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid, tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 Keylor Navas th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong khung g\u1ed7 b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 cho ai, t\u1eeb HLV Julen Lopetegui hay tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean CLB n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i.<b><span style=\"mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Keylor Navas\" title=\"Keylor Navas\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018: Keylor Navas</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Costa Rica \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i cho m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua ngay \u1edf gi\u00e2y 49, khi anh \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 pha ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat g\u00f3c h\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a Costa.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Navas ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng th\u00eam 3 l\u1ea7n trong kho\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n hai gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1nh v\u1edbi sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai khi ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n sai \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0103ng ngang c\u1ee7a Correa, khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng trong th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf hai b\u00e0n thua cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n chi\u1ec1u cao v\u00e0 s\u1ea3i tay, ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1, s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Navas th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh \u1edf Bernabeu v\u1edbi Courtois, \u0111\u00e0n em tr\u1ebb trung v\u00e0 cao l\u1edbn h\u01a1n anh \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng 6 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 14cm.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Karim Benzema v\u00e0 Gareth Bale<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Bernabeu, hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i trong b\u1ed9 tam t\u1ea5u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u1ee9 danh ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ai. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf n\u1eafm b\u1eaft c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u0129nh x\u01b0\u1edbng ti\u1ec1n tuy\u1ebfn Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">C\u1ea3 Karim Benzema v\u00e0 Gareth Bale, v\u1ed1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi d\u00f9 c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng CR7, \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale Karim Benzema\" title=\"Gareth Bale Karim Benzema\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/140738-5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018: Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 r\u1ea3nh r\u1ed7i h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, hai ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 X\u1ee9 Wales th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi t\u1eeb tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y, \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i phong \u0111\u1ed9, s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0103n \u00fd l\u1eabn nhau m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ch\u00fat g\u00ec g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 gi\u1eabm ch\u00e2n, ki\u1ec1m h\u00e3m \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Khi Bale nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb c\u00e1nh, Benzem b\u00ean trong bi\u1ebft ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb l\u00e0m g\u00ec, l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 c\u1ed9t xa c\u1ee7a khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Oblak \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00eam th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb cho Los Blancos nh\u01b0ng d\u00f9 sao, \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u00e1ng hi\u1ebfm hoi c\u0169ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i t\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng \u1edf Bernabeu. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec thay \u0111\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c trong tay t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Juanfran<o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Juanfran th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng th\u1ea7n t\u1eadn hi\u1ebfn cho Atletico Madrid su\u1ed1t bao n\u0103m qua nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chia tay \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juanfran\" title=\"Juanfran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018: Juanfran</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Marco Asensio. H\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Europa League ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khai th\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">C\u0169ng ch\u00ednh Juanfran ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai khi v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba, trong khi vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng may m\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu nh\u1edd sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a Marcelo.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">\u0110i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Juanfran mu\u00f4n ph\u1ea7n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i n\u1eb1m \u1edf vi\u1ec7c Atletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em cho Inter Milan m\u01b0\u1ee3n Sime Vrsaljko, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Croatia. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Diego Simeone s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh t\u00e2n binh Santiago Arias \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, b\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 \u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><em><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">* Theo Squawka</span></strong></em><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><br>\r\n</span></strong></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/real-madrid-vs-atletico-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-372-194560.html\">Real Madrid 2-4 Atletico: Ma c\u0169 b\u1eaft n\u1ea1t ma m\u1edbi, Atletico l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/te-nhat-sau-60-nam-lich-su-real-madrid-hlv-julen-lopetegui-noi-cung-180-194577.html\">T\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t sau 60 n\u0103m l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Real Madrid, HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u1eabn n\u00f3i c\u1ee9ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/simeone-noi-gi-sau-dai-thang-real-o-sieu-cup-chau-au-184-194592.html\">HLV Diego Simeone n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng Real Madrid \u1edf Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diego-costa-no-to-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-real-madrid-184-194584.html\">Diego Costa n\u1ed5 to sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:\n\" times=\"\" new=\"\">Gia Khoa (TTVN)</span></strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5558","checkdouble":"194606"},{"date":"15:32 16/08","title":"S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi gi\u00fap Croatia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup, Modric \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb g\u1eafn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Italia thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nInter kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Sep-Real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-Modric-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>S\u1ebfp Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1eb1ng Modric s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Modric. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac h\u01a1n \u1edf Real Madrid\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nModric \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00eam qua v\u1edbi Atletico. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n sau m\u1ed9t gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n Los Blancos b\u1ecb khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1edf c\u1eeda, tin \u0111\u1ed3n Modric r\u1eddi Real ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, ch\u00ednh ph\u00eda Inter c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Modric l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Modric t\u1eebng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Serie A thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cModric kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Inter. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u00edch th\u00fa n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf Inter. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1eb1ng Modric kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm th\u00ec mu\u1ed9n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Italia thi \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Serie A trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5557","checkdouble":"194607"},{"date":"16:43 16/08","title":"\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/11/mourinho-va-pogba-se-tim-duoc-cach-giai-quyet-mau-thuan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eabn c\u00f2n quy\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1edbi h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng 8. V\u00ec v\u1eady, Pogba v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Barca ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dimitar Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng Man United v\u1eabn d\u1ef1a kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Pogba n\u00ean s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Berbatov c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho n\u1ebfu c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/mourinho-va-pogba-se-tim-duoc-cach-giai-quyet-mau-thuan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Berbatov tin r\u1eb1ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi th\u1ea5y m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Pogba tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester. \u0110\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d, Berbatov chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi trang betfair.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf kh\u1eafp m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t, th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n qu\u1ea3 penalty ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00f3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u1ee3i khen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTruy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 b\u00e1o \u0111\u00e0i lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai. Nh\u01b0ng Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra c\u00e1ch gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nBerbatov c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng HLV Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1ed9i thu cho Man United d\u00f9 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Man United v\u00e0 Leicester s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u00edt \u1ecfi. V\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMan United \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may m\u1eafn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. Leicester c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. T\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u s\u1ef1 gi\u1eadn d\u1eef c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 1 b\u00e0n c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t th\u00ec b\u1ea1n v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i \u0111a\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5556","checkdouble":"194612"},{"date":"16:46 16/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/day-ly-do-yerry-mina-khong-toi-man-united.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Everton v\u1eeba h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 l\u00ed do v\u00ec sao h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park thay v\u00ec Man United.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t gia nh\u1eadp CLB Everton \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean 30 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, CLB Barca ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 11,8 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Mina t\u1eeb Palmeiras.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Day!-Ly-do-Yerry-Mina-khong-toi-Man-United-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes l\u00e0 hai ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.&nbsp;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Goodison Park, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB M.U theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Anh, Everton th\u1eafng trong v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u00ec ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi cho Jair, ng\u01b0\u1eddi &nbsp;\u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mina c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fa c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n Man United. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Everton, Marcel Brands&nbsp;\u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">GI\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do Yerry Mina kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Man United, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y cho r\u1eb1ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Everton: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed m\u00f4i gi\u1edbi \u1edf m\u1ee9c b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi mua v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd chi cho 1 v\u1ee5 mua s\u1eafm. Barcelona c\u0169ng th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Man United nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua mua Mina.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, Mina \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t ki\u00ean \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi t\u00f4i: &lsquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Everton&rsquo;. T\u00f4i h\u01a1i lo l\u1eafng v\u00ec s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Man United nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng k\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mina v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t l\u00ed do gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c Mina t\u1edbi Everton l\u00e0 v\u00ec anh mu\u1ed1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n thay v\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh cho su\u1ea5t ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Old Trafford. Ngo\u00e0i ra vi\u1ec7c Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea7n ch\u1eeb gi\u1eefa quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua trung v\u1ec7 Colombia v\u00e0 ch\u1edd Leicester nh\u1ea3 Harry Maguire c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-vui-tu-hang-cong-truoc-tran-gap-brighton-172-194551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/4/mu-don-tin-vui-tu-hang-cong-truoc-tran-gap-brighton.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-don-tin-vui-tu-hang-cong-truoc-tran-gap-brighton-172-194551.html\">MU \u0111\u00f3n tin vui t\u1eeb h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brighton</span><br>\r\nHLV Jose Mourinho \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brighton cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea-172-194549.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea-172-194549.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Wilfried Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\">Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o danh ti\u1ebfng LEquipe (Ph\u00e1p) v\u1eeba loan tin r\u1eb1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Zinedine Zidane mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Premier League v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng m\u00e0 Mourinho...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5555","checkdouble":"194617"},{"date":"09:11 16/08","title":"C\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam: \u201cNepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/cuu-hlv-truong-dt-viet-nam-nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eafc n\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nam \u00c1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/9/HLV-Phan-Thanh-Hung-Nepal-khong-co-cua-so-voi-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Zing.vn: &quot;R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00f3p \u00fd \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111ang ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t. Ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec Nepal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1eeda so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee9 t\u1ef1 tin \u0111\u00e1, v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 n\u00ean \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 h\u1ebft l\u00f2ng cho h\u1ecd&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u00eam v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh n\u00f3i: &quot;Ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t so v\u1edbi t\u1ea7m ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi chinh chi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u t\u1ea1i V.League, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00ean t\u1eadp trung c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua. Sau n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi theo \u00f4ng, t\u00e2m l\u00fd thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y m\u1ed7i khi b\u01b0\u1edbc ra s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n nay l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i trong t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal &ndash; \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-muon-nepal-da-doi-cong-voi-olympic-viet-nam-168-194546.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo mu\u1ed1n Nepal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ec1u 15/8, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb \u0110T Olympic Nepal.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/u23-nepal-cung-co-thu-mon-quoc-dan-nhu-bui-tien-dung-472-194545.html\">U23 Nepal c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n nh\u01b0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nU23 Nepal, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018, c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c d\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng: Kiran Chemjong Limbu.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5554","checkdouble":"194590"},{"date":"11:05 16/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/2/olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-co-hoi-cho-kep-phu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u00e0 ai s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3?</h2><h2>Khi xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y hai h\u00f4m, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nepal v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 15/8. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 n\u00f3i: \u201c\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn\u00a0U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e0i s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Pakistan.\u00a0T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1eafng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111a s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh v\u1edbi nhau t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho k\u00e9p ph\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/Olympic-Viet-Nam-vs-Olympic-Nepal-Co-hoi-cho-kep-phu-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0vs Olympic Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c xoay tua \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y Park t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y tr\u00e1nh b\u1ecb th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eaft b\u00e0i n\u1ebfu ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n h\u1ebft, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh trong to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, khi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m trong m\u1eaft ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p Nepal, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang c\u00f3 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y, HLV Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ai s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i?<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong h\u00e0ng trung v\u1ec7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do \u0111\u00f3, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi V\u0103n L\u1ee3i. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1eafng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t C\u1ea3ng. Ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Xuan Manh choi cuc hay trong tran tu ket voi U23 Iraq\" title=\"Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi U23 Iraq\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/31/Hau-ve-Xuan-Manh-mong-mau-co-tien-thuong-de-tra-no-cho-bo-me-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh t\u1eebng ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c hay t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n v\u1ec1 Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y sau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u1eeba qua. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i V-League n\u0103m nay, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng, v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7. \u00a0Do \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang d\u00e0nh cho \u0110\u1ee9c Huy v\u00e0 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 Quang H\u1ea3i l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n xuy\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Song r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i quen thu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea9y V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1eafm thay cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c. L\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c anh v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Wibawa Mukti, T\u00e2y Java (Indonesia) v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h.vn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn, m\u1eddi qu\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 quan t\u00e2m theo d\u00f5i./.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal:</strong><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n L\u1ee3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Nepal: Kiran Chemjong, Tamang, Chaudhary, Shrestha, Budhathoki, Rohit Chand, Gurung, Bista, Magar, Bharat Khawas, Magar.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang-168-194581.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal (19h ng\u00e0y 16/8): Duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng</span><br>\r\nG\u1eb7p Nepal \u2013 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 s\u1edbm v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec ng\u00f4i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-olympic-viet-nam-vs-olympic-nepal-19h-ngay-168-duy-tri-ngoi-dau-bang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-olympic-viet-nam-lai-vao-chung-ket-duoc-chu-sao-khong-168-194536.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9, sao kh\u00f4ng?</span><br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 tin th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhat-ban-thang-nhe-nepal-thoi-co-vang-cho-olympic-viet-nam-168-194550.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal: Th\u1eddi c\u01a1 v\u00e0ng cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng nh\u1eb9 Nepal \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u00f2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5553","checkdouble":"194598"},{"date":"11:38 16/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-cu-tro-ly-do-tham-han-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho hai tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd t\u1edbi xem, ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 6-0 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain h\u00f4m qua 15/8.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1edbi Indonesia v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5m HC v\u00e0ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ed1n n\u0103m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 kim chi s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jo Hyeon-woo, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hwang Ui-jo v\u00e0 Son Heung-min - ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 Bahrain, Malaysia v\u00e0 Kyrgyzstan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Vi\u1ec7t Nam, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 hai b\u1ea3ng D, s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1ea5m HC v\u00e0ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam \u1edf Asiad 2018 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Park Hang-seo c\u1ea9n tr\u1ecdng chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u01b0 li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c thu th\u1eadp video c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd di chuy\u1ec3n h\u01a1n 100 kilom\u00e9t t\u1eeb n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf Cikarang, t\u1edbi Bandung \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Bahrain. Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd L\u01b0u Danh Minh xem v\u00e0 ghi ch\u00e9p v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Young Sub th\u00ec ghi h\u00ecnh to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1eed tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam do th\u00e1m H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/A1-3022-1534383659.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Young Sub khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111i Bandung ghi h\u00ecnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ea1y, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 phi\u00ean d\u1ecbch ti\u1ebfng Anh cho HLV Park Hang-seo. \u1ea2nh Vnexpress</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang-seo kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c cho c\u00e1c tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd, ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u00f4m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. Ngay c\u1ea3 Young Sub, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m vai tr\u00f2 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean ti\u1ebfng Anh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, c\u0169ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, \u0111i ghi h\u00ecnh theo d\u00f5i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong ng\u00e0y HLV Park Hang-seo c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i do th\u00e1m, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng v\u00e0 th\u1eafng Bahrain 6-0. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm l\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng, n\u00ean r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1 ra m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean c\u1ea3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D b\u1edfi trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang-seo \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pakistan 3-0 trong khi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. T\u1ed1i nay 16/8, Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t mong Nepal s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 HLV c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1. Khi \u0111\u00f3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c\u201d, HLV Park Hang-seo chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c e ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eed th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Vnexpress.net<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5552","checkdouble":"194601"},{"date":"09:25 16/08","title":"Griezmann: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/griezmann-toi-da-dung-khi-o-lai-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Griezmann kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>Atletico th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real</h2>\r\nGriezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barcelona trong v\u00f2ng 2 n\u0103m qua. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid trong m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. T\u1ea1i Nga, Grizou \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap Les Bleus \u0111\u0103ng quang v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Griezmann T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00fang khi \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/griezmann-toi-da-dung-khi-o-lai-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGriezmann kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u cho Atletico \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00eam qua v\u1edbi Real. Anh ch\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 57 ph\u00fat do th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c ch\u01b0a \u1ed5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Diego Costa v\u00e0 hai b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Saul v\u00e0 Koke trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Atletico gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng vang d\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real.\r\n<h2>Griezmann vui m\u1eebng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</h2>\r\nHLV Diego Simeone gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Atletico v\u1edbi 7 danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 Griezmann ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o Simeone l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>&ldquo;T\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, v\u00e0o Simeone. H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t khi m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng hai \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t 100% th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean. Th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t khi kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y&rdquo;.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5551","checkdouble":"194588"}]}